name: County Road 550 Vinyl Sticker
description:
Have you ever stopped into Phil's 550 on a beer or toilet paper run? How about attempting to wade across to Little Presque Isle with your camping gear balanced precariously on your head? And I don't think we need to mention the Big Bay Mud Drags, the Lumberjack or Hogsback.

'550' is more than just a road, it represents how 'Yoopers' do summer.

If you know what we mean, pick up a few of these stickers and slap em' somewhere that will make you proud!

These 4.25" x 4.24" stickers are made of high-quality vinyl and designed to withstand even the worst outdoor weather.

name: County Road 550 Men's T-shirt
description:
This comfortable, 100% cotton t-shirt will quickly become your go-to shirt for a variety of occasions. The shallow v-neck design looks good as a stand-alone or under other shirts.

If you know it, rep it!
